                <a href="http://dirk.eddelbuettel.com/blog/code/rcpp">/code/rcpp</a>  |  
                <a href="http://dirk.eddelbuettel.com/blog/2023/01/29#rcpptoml_0.2.2">permanent link</a>
              </p>
	      
